{"tid":2183393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅稱韋德齊訪台將付出代價，在台捷克人反嗆「去死吧」","createTime":"2020-09-01T02:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T03:27:24.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7114c72fd97eabb2b7a745f21c23a40a78cea814","tid":2183393,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/01/phpGrgUp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F01%2FphpGrgUp5.jpg&h=c5dd88e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕捷克參議院議長韋德齊日前率團訪台，卻被中國外交部長王毅批評是「公開挑釁」，揚言會讓韋德齊及背後的反華勢力付出「沉重代價」。而王毅的發言也引起捷克外長佩崔傑克不滿，在台北經營捷克餐酒館的捷克籍老闆皮哈（Karel Picha）則直言：「大部分捷克人應該會對他說『去死吧』。」<br />\n<br />\n根據《美國之音》報導，皮哈提到，由於蘇聯共產黨占領捷克長達30年，對捷克人的傷害太深，因此捷克人民只要聽到有任何一個共產國家威脅捷克，「我們就會恨得咬牙切齒」。<br />\n<br />\n皮哈表示，雖然捷克政府和總統並未公開支持韋德齊訪台，但官方也絕對不會喜歡被威脅或是主權被侵害，然而大部分捷克人民也不會害怕被中國報復，尤其是捷克的經濟其實並不依賴中國。"},{"pid":"2779debe5ac2a862da5916bfc0bbf32b5794a508","tid":2183393,"uid":31320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFRvQCX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFRvQCX.gif&h=2065b7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnumcRi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnumcRi.gif&h=8065ac86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/djGLEwk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdjGLEwk.gif&h=64c88298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e010tpG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe010tpG.gif&h=b8d4254f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CUEJX2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CUEJX2.gif&h=bd96cbb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b4113fe8569ec63d8b91bee9a113a677d4a8d5c","tid":2183393,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"香港有冇捷克菜呢？"}]}